so everything is going by quick.. the other day i looked at the calendar and there was 44 days left of school. now i look- 19... tell me that isnt crazy?!? any who.. i am finally enjoying highschool. grad bash was awesome! I mean.. yea, I had bad luck, because a lot of things happened to me, and no one else. lol.. but other than that, i enjoyed it. i have gotten extremely close to those that make my last days of high school rock! and i love it. i look back and laugh.. because all the shit and drama that cause stress upon your life is something you'll forget once you graduate. ten years from now, what do you think you'll remember most? not all the drama... but all of the smiles, and laughs you have spent with your closest friends. you might not remember what you wore, or your friends names (although that sounds harsh), but you will remember you had a blast when you were with them. at one point in my life i thought SMSH = DRAMA
but now... SMSH = LOVE

it was fun.

I had so much fun last night. I had to work a party for my mom and I ended up acting like I attended the party rather than working it. My uncle was the bartender and he hooked us up with so many drinks. My favorite were the Apple Martinis and the Liquid Cocaine Shots. 

Good News is I made $220 in one night. How cool is that?!

I went to sleep at like 5:30 AM, and woke up at 9:45 AM... lol-that was funny. I felt like throwing up, but I was still kind of out of it. What Ever. I never drink, so when I do I get bad as hell. My Tia was hilarious she had to pee and she didnt want to go to the bathroom, she almost peed her pants! hahaha


well Happy New Years Everyone! Hope you had FUN!

[edit] 
i myself am in my first real relationship with a guy named gio, who is immature, annoying, and has problems, yet very humorous, caring, intelligent, and has a strong personallity... if you could find someone and accept every part of him then you found the "one"  .... right? or just maybe mr. right now.. but really that is all i want at the moment-- i dont want to look at the future, make plans, or have hopes and dreams... i just want to live day after day wondering whats going to happen next... 


i dont plan on having someone write my life story-i want it to happen by itself, like me typing this lj update

that's how i think a person should live their life.
